# Coding Standards (编码规范)

Scope: all DTS source code

## General

- All source files use UTF-8 encoding, LF line endings.
- Maximum line length: 120 characters.
- All public APIs must have documentation (docstring/javadoc/godoc).
- No hardcoded secrets, credentials, or environment-specific URLs in source code.
- Use environment variables or config files for all environment-specific values.

## Python (AI Core)

- Python >= 3.12
- Formatter: ruff format
- Linter: ruff check
- Type hints required on all function signatures.
- Async-first: use async/await for I/O-bound operations.
- Dependencies managed via pyproject.toml + uv lock.
- gRPC service implementations in `services/` directory.
- Business logic in `core/` directory, framework-agnostic.
- Tests in `tests/` mirroring source structure.

## Java (Business Platform)

- Java 21 LTS + Spring Boot 3.x
- Formatter: google-java-format
- Linter: checkstyle (Google style)
- Package structure: `com.dts.<service>.<layer>` (controller/service/repository/model/proto)
- Use records for DTOs and value objects.
- Repository pattern for all database access.
- gRPC service definitions in shared proto module.
- No field injection (@Autowired on fields). Use constructor injection only.
- Tests: JUnit 5 + Mockito. Integration tests use Testcontainers.

## Go (Infrastructure)

- Go >= 1.22
- Formatter: gofmt
- Linter: golangci-lint
- Follow standard Go project layout (cmd/ internal/ pkg/ api/).
- Error handling: wrap errors with context using fmt.Errorf("...: %w", err).
- K8s Operator: use controller-runtime framework.
- CLI: use cobra + viper.
- Tests: standard testing package + testify for assertions.

## Frontend (React)

- TypeScript strict mode.
- Formatter: prettier
- Linter: eslint (flat config)
- Component structure: one component per file, named export.
- State management: Zustand for global, React state for local.
- Data fetching: TanStack Query v5.
- Styling: Tailwind CSS utility classes only. No CSS modules, no styled-components.
- Banned dependencies: antd, @vanilla-extract/*, styled-components, @iconify/react, apexcharts, date-fns.
